{"tid":1553824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足換完衫之後見到防暴","createTime":"2019-09-08T17:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T18:01:01.000Z","uid":172382,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6c8da13390c0155ef9f16167624d723233d9b5","tid":1553824,"uid":172382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好跑呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當你換完衫同埋dum曬啲裝之後你就係一個普通市民，正常情況之下普通市民一見到防暴係唔會即刻跑㗎嘛，你一跑佢就追你要去制服你，唔會理得你着咩衫<br />\n<br />\n所以手足換完衫dum完裝之後一定要做返個普通市民，路過嘅繼續行，等車嘅繼續等，保持冷靜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9f7d7d65d036aebbac3928414fb4823ea3b7b5","tid":1553824,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"[急!!!]9/9有班中學生等緊你地救！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"52ddf2d124d734d21694b19b995f12070efead01","tid":1553824,"uid":172382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1f6e3b4a061c70bb02332858840cb3789d4bd030","tid":1553824,"uid":172382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b9c42b2ff2d54fd476b20c1ff4a38cd88a372daf","tid":1553824,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8fdbf1a8589addf7bce673a1775c9601e87772f","tid":1553824,"uid":172382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ad852c66dadb017d968d61aefb15f394e6fb2e92","tid":1553824,"uid":14880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b9c42b2ff2d54fd476b20c1ff4a38cd88a372daf","tid":1553824,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy